Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:01.80,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)\pos(575,300)}夏海的雙打
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:21.64,NEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向雨許願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれそうな夢の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:34.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}よろこびを探す世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:44.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君はどんな輝きで　明日へと跳ぶの？　教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:50.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}声になった未来の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:56.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まりの my melody 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:01:02.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY！ 空が青く高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:07.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙ぐんだ今を忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:13.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひたすら進もうと誓うから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分かりあった瞬間は大切な
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an7}ずっと一緒に　君と一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:35.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:40.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:46.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:34.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:44.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:56.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:01:02.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:07.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:13.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:17.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:35.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:40.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:46.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:50.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:53.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:20.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我的手握起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一天又隨著夕陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆一樣漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:25.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大樹  早飯已經做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯就把冰箱裏的東西熱一下吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始家裏只有你和大樹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到後天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明要參加社團還要學習忙死了  他卻一點都不來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道埋頭打遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子不都是這樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他站在能否成為男子漢的十字路口時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為姐姐的我必須給他正確的指導吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攔的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海她們要等社團活動結束後再來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過那麼長時間  你們已經很合拍了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假期內就要搬家了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  暫定在月末的時候搬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季在這裏剩下的時間也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就稍微陪她一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  過來集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天的練習賽定在下午一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油啊  我們會來看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些考生還有更加重要的事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有在好好學習的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田水野組合果然是由我們來對付嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能為我們報仇雪恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇雪恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在給學妹增加什麼壓力啊  真是兩個過分的學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可已經打進了縣大賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭  我們是在開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太認真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  既然上了就要以勝利為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺狀態也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁固然也很重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑現在的狀態我覺得很有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有覺得還沒打夠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意下如何  和我們打個加時賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想緩解一下暑期補課的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要和我們打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海姑且不說  主戰力的紗季不在搞的作業一點進展都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她意識到反正自己要轉校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作業什麼的已經沒有做的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都說過要來幫忙了 應該不會那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒回我的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  優香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  凜  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  媽媽在叫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天人手不夠 趕快去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  3x+y=9 2x+y=7
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兩個算式合二為一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且算是和你說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發球失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束  4比1  淺野石田組合獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺完全力不從心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們是不是專門盯著夏海在打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為相澤她比較容易對付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢澤擊球不錯  體力和爆發力也超群  但打法很單純  很容易回擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水越完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的我好像很不單純一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在誇獎你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打法很單純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆  要打到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好要一起做作業的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是要去優香家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我家稍微有點不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  今天不要做作業了  去KTV為歌手大會做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思  你難不成是準備要參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  我們是以成為偶像為目標的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手大會冠軍什麼的自然是手到擒來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姑且還是要練習一下的  你們會去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  我得回去做晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始媽媽不在家  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  怎麼這樣  大樹什麼的讓他吃泡麵不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不能這麼做  下回見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  不是說好要一起創造回憶的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海說她的媽媽要後天才能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到那時為止都要像現在這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天還有網球社的練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺只有夏海一個人會很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯是姐姐來做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  難道你要來做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給我乖乖地等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要許什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為夏海而許的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  做家務  參加社團活動  和優香她們做暑假作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽  好想贏下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和紗季搭檔參加比賽這也是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的球比較容易回擊到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  你怎麼又泡進去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大樹那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有點泡暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  喂  我的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？  有沒有什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事啦  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先穿衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這無論怎麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是「那個」的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  現在狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底許了什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成兩個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在房間裏  把窗簾拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  快點  你看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的變成兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  哪個是正牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是正牌貨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  你才是贗品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月1日巨蟹座A型血  體重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,44KG
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三圍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上到下  77 59 78
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個都挺像夏海的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你從剛才開始就很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季姐  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼鑽到被窩裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  叫你不要隨便把門打開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是從被子裏傳出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是肚子叫了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是自己 同步率真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香是你出的餿主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上來我家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話什麼的之後再打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  反正過一陣子就變回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了  你給再過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被子蓋的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 姐姐 我的早飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  昨晚一直被差遣到半夜 累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道這樣把我變成兩個人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎  夏海真的變成兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢擅自把我變成兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  既然都已經變了那也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}夏海  你幹嘛這麼用力打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是現在就要合理利用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那個我為了比賽全身心地投入到社團活動中去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏海就負責做作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  還有家事之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是紗季不在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使夏海在  戰鬥力上也沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天失誤貌似多了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為用的力道比平時大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為昨天被淺野學姐們說了才這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽就在明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才想要改變打法  那根本不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還差一點點就能找到感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我自己練一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  明天是Candle cafe的第一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs14}（Candle cafe：下田市夏日祭典的一環，\N屆時會把寫上願望燭燈裝飾在河岸邊。\N此活動由咖啡店candle cafe冠名）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上比賽已經結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 作業的進展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(130,355}紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,355}等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教教我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 來得正好 快輔導我做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一個人留在那裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她說今天要強化練習大力擊球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎  感覺分配得很合理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要多做點作業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這樣轉換的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把注意力集中到一點上  結果使自己的視野變窄了是你的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網球也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這樣就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 剛才有誰在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像一直都是我在躲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很困嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的比賽沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特訓過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒狀態的話就馬上交換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說今天一天和你拉開了很大差距
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就僅僅一天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 泡得有點暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓大樹發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累得睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她集中精神練了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過把注意力集中到一點上 結果使自己的視野變窄了是我的壞習慣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說網球也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能更詳細的告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的網球太過於以自己為中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過於以自己為中心？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更注意對手的站位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說對手是攻方 當接發球的位置比較靠前的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候第一次回球就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2比0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加 要更加用力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3比0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意別在意  回敬她們一球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被壓著打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如紗季所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想著自己所決定的事  看不到全局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得好  上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本局結束  交換場地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  被得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙發失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0比1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急 一球一球的扳回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天紗季告訴我的事情 現在好想告訴那個我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在出現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現夏海有兩個的話會引起大騷亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0比2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0比3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點  笨蛋夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季  我們來昨天你說的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:19:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海 打得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:19:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}1比3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接再厲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當兩個人的我變回一個人時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}好難受 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺閉塞的視野好像一下子變廣闊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體是由一直在練習的我來驅動 但是頭腦卻很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著紗季教給我的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半雖然有挽回比分  但沒能反超啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一場比賽  能贏下來該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和出席了縣大賽的組合幾乎是勢均力敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺野學姐們也表揚了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想說很期待下次  但聽說你要轉學了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你還是有機會再打的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如若夢境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的在哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了好多心願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都實現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,minako,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望能過個開心的夏天 夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,ayahi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}希望大家能身體健康 紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,haruka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}一定要成為偶像 優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,aki,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}希望能有許許多多的人來參拜我們神社 環凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人寫的都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為偶像啦 偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是歌手大會 優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的願望從某種意義上來說已經實現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 發生了很多開心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些沒法寫在日記上的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  變成兩個人什麼的  這種事一般是無法體驗到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次讓你體驗一下變成小動物的美妙感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣或許會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想她變成什麼動物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袋熊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又抽又扣地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 看過之後感覺自己也能打網球了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看著是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你想  想像訓練是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.78,0:24:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像自己行動的樣子也是訓練的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就來看Four season的DVD吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你就是想偷懶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  想像訓練  想像訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇跡  第七話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.61,0:24:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向雨許願
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往偶像之路也是從想像訓練開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體要動才行啊！
